articles.title: Trump says he's firing Fed Governor Lisa Cook, opening new front in fight for central bank control
articles.description: President Trump said Monday night that he's firing Federal Reserve governor Lisa Cook, an unprecedented move that would constitute a sharp escalation in his battle to exert greater control over what has long been considered an independent institution [1, 4].

articles.title: Exhibit shines light on African American veterans
articles.description: At Dallas College's Cliff Gallery, "Honor Endures" showcases portraits by Keith Vinson and others that honor the lives, struggles, and strength of African American service members [3].
